india-vs-china-asian-games-2023-football-match-live-score-updates-4403827%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Parliament%2C%20Day%201%3A%20M%20Kharge%20vs%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20On%20GST%2C%20Women's%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%2C%20triggered%20a%20huge%20war%20of%20words%20between%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Union%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20today.%20Speaking%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged%20that%20the%20reservation%20will%20only%20be%20manipulated%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20choose%20uneducated%20voiceless%20women%20who%20are%20unequipped%20for%20the%20task.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20parliamentarians%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20vehemently%20objected.%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20making%20%26quot%3Bsweeping%20statements%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLiteracy%20rate%20of%20women%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20is%20less%20and%20that%20is%20why%20political%20parties%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20choosing%20weak%20women.%20They%20never%20choose%20those%20who%20are%20educated%20and%20can%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20treasury%20benches%20started%20protest%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20shouted%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20half%20ticket%3F%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20one-third%20ticket...%20Sit%20down%20and%20be%20quiet...%20I%20have%20an%20idea%20how%20backward%2C%20Scheduled%20Caste%20people%20are%20chosen%20by%20parties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20but%20to%20make%20a%20sweeping%20statement%20that%20all%20parties%20choose%20women%20who%20are%20not%20effective%20is%20absolutely%20unacceptable.%20We%20all%20have%20been%20empowered%20by%20our%20party%2C%20by%20our%20Prime%20Minister.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20is%20an%20empowered%20woman.%20Every%20MP%20of%20our%20party%20is%20an%20empowered%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20sweeping%20statements%2C%20she%20added%2C%20might%20apply%20to%20Congress%20even%20though%20it%20had%20women%20presidents.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20object%20to%20him%20making%20a%20sweeping%20generalisation%20of%20all%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20who%20are%20from%20backward%20classes.%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20do%20not%20have%20the%20opportunities%20which%20she%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20Mr%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUndaunted%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20shouted%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20the%20President%3F%20I%20am%20Opposition%20leader%20cannot%20insult%20people%20like%20this...%20Cannot%20draw%20differentiation%20between%20women%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20had%20clashed%20over%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%2C%20with%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleging%20that%20the%20states%20are%20not%20receiving%20their%20share%20of%20revenue%20and%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bweakening%26quot%3B%20of%20federalism%20.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20had%20roundly%20objected%2C%20insisting%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20is%20owed%20to%20any%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20leaders%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20give%20their%20statements%20in%20writing%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20by%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20years.%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20called%20it%20a%20bill%20to%20fool%20women%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20the%20well-being%20and%20welfare%20of%20women.%20%26quot%3BA%20closer%20reading%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20bill%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20'Mahila%20Bewakoof%20Banao'%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20offers%20women%2033%20reservation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%20The%20reservation%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20a%20delimitation%20exercise%20is%20undertaken%20and%20will%20continue%20for%2015%20years.%20Seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20will%20be%20rotated%20after%20each%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20the%20bill%20in%20his%20opening%20speech%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament.%20In%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20without%20naming%20the%20party%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BParliament%20has%20tried%20(to%20pass%20the%20bill)%20in%20the%20past%20too...%20there%20have%20been%20discussions%20around%20women's%20reservations%20for%20years.%20Can%20say%20with%20pride%20we%20have%20scripted%20history%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20historic%20shift%2C%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20shifted%20to%20the%20new%20building%20on%20Delhi's%20Central%20Vista%20today%2C%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20an%20era.%C2%A0%20The%20old%20British-era%20building%2C%20where%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20met%20to%20frame%20the%20Constitution%2C%20will%20be%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BSamvidhan%20Sadan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695124080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9i3c76u_mallikarjun-kharge-new-parliament-pti-650-_650x400_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-1-new-parliament-m-kharge-vs-nirmala-sitharaman-on-gst-womens-bill-4404018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposed%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%2C%20triggered%20a%20huge%20war%20of%20words%20between%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Union%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-1-new-parliament-m-kharge-vs-nirmala-sitharaman-on-gst-womens-bill-4404018%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-1-new-parliament-m-kharge-vs-nirmala-sitharaman-on-gst-womens-bill-4404018%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-1-new-parliament-m-kharge-vs-nirmala-sitharaman-on-gst-womens-bill-4404018%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Begging%20Before%20The%20World%20While%20India%20Reached%20Moon%3A%20Nawaz%20Sharif%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20self-exiled%20former%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20has%20said%20that%20his%20country%20is%20begging%20money%20from%20the%20world%20while%20India%20has%20reached%20the%20moon%20and%20hosted%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20blaming%20the%20country's%20former%20generals%20and%20judges%20for%20its%20economic%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20economy%20has%20been%20in%20a%20free%20fall%20mode%20for%20the%20last%20many%20years%2C%20bringing%20untold%20pressure%20on%20the%20poor%20masses%20in%20the%20form%20of%20unchecked%20double-digit%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20Pakistan's%20prime%20minister%20goes%20country%20to%20country%20to%20beg%20for%20funds%20while%20India%20has%20reached%20the%20moon%20and%20is%20holding%20G20%20meetings.%20Why%20Pakistan%20couldn't%20achieve%20the%20feats%20India%20did.%20Who%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20asked%20while%20addressing%20a%20party%20meeting%20in%20Lahore%20from%20London%20via%20video%20link%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20became%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20it%20had%20only%20a%20billion%20dollars%20in%20kitty%20but%20now%20India's%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20have%20risen%20up%20to%20%24600%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20questioned%20where%20India%20has%20reached%20today%20and%20where%20Pakistan%20is%20left%20behind%20begging%20the%20world%20for%20some%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20IMF%20transferred%20USD%201.2%20billion%20to%20cash-strapped%20Pakistan%2C%20part%20of%20the%20USD%203%20billion%20bailout%20programme%20for%20nine%20months%20to%20support%20the%20government's%20efforts%20to%20stabilise%20the%20country's%20ailing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif%20has%20for%20the%20first%20time%20announced%20his%20return%20to%20the%20country%20on%20October%2021%20to%20lead%20the%20party's%20political%20campaign%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20ending%20his%20over%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202019%2C%20Sharif%2C%20serving%20a%20seven-year%20jail%20term%20in%20AlAzizia%20Mills%20corruption%20case%2C%20was%20helped%20by%20the%20then%20army%20chief%20Gen%20Bajwa%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20on%20medical%20grounds.%20The%20PML-N%20says%20it%20will%20secure%20a%20protective%20bail%20for%20him%20before%20his%20arrival%20to%20Lahore%20next%20month.%20His%20party%20has%20planned%20a%20historic%20welcome%20on%20his%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20military%20and%20judicial%20establishment%20of%202017%20whom%20he%20termed%20responsible%20for%20sending%20him%20home%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man%20(Nawaz)%20who%20rid%20the%20country%20of%20power%20load%20shedding%20was%20sent%20home%20by%20four%20judges%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20said%20in%20his%20emotional%20speech.%20He%20added%20that%20then-army%20chief%20General%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%20and%20then%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%20chief%20General%20Faiz%20Hamid%20were%20behind%20his%20ouster.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Former)%20chief%20justices%20Saqib%20Nisar%20and%20Asif%20Saeed%20Khosa%20were%20tools%20of%20%5Bthe%20former%20army%20chief%20and%20his%20spy%20chief%5D.%20Their%20crime%20is%20bigger%20than%20a%20murder%20offence.%20Giving%20them%20pardons%20will%20be%20an%20injustice%20to%20the%20nation.%20They%20don't%20deserve%20pardon%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20said%2C%20vowing%20to%20hold%20them%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20'characters'%20who%20unleashed%20economic%20misery%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20will%20have%20to%20face%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pledged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif%20also%20declared%20that%20his%20party%20will%20win%20in%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20some%20former%20aides%20to%20Sharif's%20PML-N%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20caretaker%20federal%20cabinet%2C%20and%20the%20party%20(PMLN)%20is%20not%20joining%20the%20demand%20to%20hold%20elections%20within%2090%20days%20after%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20assemblies%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples'%20Party%20(PPP)%20of%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20suspects%20the%20Sharifs%20of%20cosying%20up%20to%20the%20powerful%20military%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20PPP%20leaders%20have%20accused%20the%20PML-N%20of%20becoming%20a%20'darling%20of%20the%20military'%20and%20conspiring%20against%20its%20former%20allies%20to%20gain%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695123840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Ftvnofip8_nawaz-sharif-reuters_625x300_07_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-begging-before-the-world-while-india-reached-moon-nawaz-sharif-4404133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharif%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20military%20and%20judicial%20establishment%20of%202017%20whom%20he%20termed%20responsible%20for%20sending%20him%20home%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20prime%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2