ir%20work%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmsrc.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2F2023%2F09%2Fmicrosoft-mitigated-exposure-of-internal-information-in-a-storage-account-due-to-overly-permissive-sas-token%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20said%20the%20team%20was%20trying%20to%20share%20open-source%20training%20data%20on%20the%20software%20development%20platform%20GitHub%2C%20as%20is%20common%20behavior%20in%20the%20AI%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20cybersecurity%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiz.io%2Fblog%2F38-terabytes-of-private-data-accidentally-exposed-by-microsoft-ai-researchers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWiz%3C%2Fa%3E%20discovered%20that%20the%20researchers%20accidentally%20gave%20people%20access%20to%2038%20terabytes%20worth%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20Microsoft%20researchers'%20GitHub%20repository%20told%20users%20to%20download%20AI%20models%20from%20a%20cloud%20storage%20URL.%20But%20the%20link%20had%20been%20misconfigured%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20granted%20permissions%20across%20the%20entire%20storage%20account%2C%20according%20to%20Wiz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWiz%20found%20that%20the%20account%20included%20Microsoft%20employees'%20personal%20computer%20backups%2C%20passwords%20to%20Microsoft%20services%2C%20secret%20keys%2C%20and%20over%2030%2C000%20internal%20Teams%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20customer%20data%20was%20exposed%2C%20and%20no%20other%20internal%20services%20were%20put%20at%20risk%20because%20of%20this%20issue.%20No%20customer%20action%20is%20required%20in%20response%20to%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said%20in%20Monday's%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20sharing%20the%20learnings%20and%20best%20practices%20below%20to%20inform%20our%20customers%20and%20help%20them%20avoid%20similar%20incidents%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp