tails%20Of%20New%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20becoming%20law%20after%20nearly%20three%20decades%20of%20stalling%20and%20discord.%20However%2C%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%2C%20as%20promised%20by%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20may%20come%20into%20force%20only%20by%202029%2C%20NDTV%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20quota%20can%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20the%20first%20delimitation%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20after%20the%20bill%20becomes%20law%2C%20according%20to%20details%20exclusively%20accessed%20by%20NDTV.%20Constituencies%20will%20be%20redrawn%20only%20after%20the%20next%20Census%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%2082%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20amended%20in%202002%2C%20says%20the%20delimitation%20process%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20based%20on%20the%20first%20Census%20taken%20after%202026.%20Originally%2C%20the%20first%20Census%20after%202026%20was%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20in%202031%2C%20which%20would%20be%20followed%20by%20delimitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Census%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20held%20last%20in%202021%2C%20but%20was%20delayed%20because%20of%20Covid%2C%20so%20the%20next%20count%20might%20be%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20enable%20the%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20sooner%2C%20Article%2082%20has%20to%20be%20amended.%20However%2C%20southern%20states%20are%20against%20the%20immediate%20delimitation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20quota%20bill%20will%20be%20in%20force%20for%2015%20years%20after%20becoming%20an%20Act%2C%20but%20its%20term%20can%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20will%20be%20rotated%20after%20each%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20six-page%20bill%20says%20a%20third%20of%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assemblies%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20and%20filled%20by%20direct%20election.%20Also%2C%20the%20quota%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20or%20state%20Legislative%20Councils.%20Within%20the%20quota%2C%20a%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20will%20be%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20does%20not%20include%20reservation%20for%20OBCs%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%2C%20as%20such%20a%20provision%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20the%20legislature.%20This%20was%20the%20demand%20over%20which%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20opposed%20the%20women's%20quota%20bill%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20drafted%20in%202010%20when%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20Congress%20government%20was%20in%20power.%20Only%2C%20two%20amendments%20to%20bring%20in%20quota%20for%20the%20Anglo-Indian%20community%20have%20been%20dropped%20in%20the%20new%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20provisions%20of%20the%20women's%20quota%20bill%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20delimitation%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20after%20%26quot%3Bthe%20relevant%20figures%20for%20the%20first%20Census%20taken%20after%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Act%202023%20have%20been%20published%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20cease%20to%20have%20effect%2015%20years%20after%20its%20enactment%2C%20says%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEffectively%2C%20the%20new%20bill%20is%20an%20enabling%20provision%2C%20a%20step%20forward%2C%20but%20a%20separate%20bill%20and%20notification%20will%20be%20needed%20for%20the%20delimitation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubject%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20articles%20239A%2C%20330A%2C%20and%20332A%2C%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20a%20State%2C%20and%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Del%20shall%20continue%20till%20such%20date%20as%20the%20Parliament%20may%20by%20law%20determine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons%20says%20the%20bill%20seeks%20greater%20participation%20of%20women%20as%20public%20representatives%20in%20policy-making%20at%20the%20state%20and%20national%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20women%20only%20make%20up%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20parliament%20and%20legislatures%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20far%20lower%20than%20the%20world%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695119880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fljifo6ns_narendra-modi-cabinet-meet_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20becoming%20law%20after%20nearly%20three%20decades%20of%20stalling%20and%20discord.%20However%2C%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%2C%20as%20promised%20by%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20may%20come%20into%20force%20only%20by%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20are%20some%20Sikhs%20calling%20for%20a%20separate%20homeland%20in%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695119777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2