al%20legislature%20and%2050%20out%20of%20350%20seats%20in%20its%20'Jatiya%20Sangsad'%20are%20reserved%20for%20women.%20The%20current%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20the%20country's%20parliament%20is%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%2033.09%2C%20the%20percentage%20is%20much%20better%20for%20Nepal%2C%20but%20very%20close%20to%20the%20one-third%20seats%20for%20women%20that%20had%20been%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%202007.%20The%20lower%20house%20of%20the%20Nepal%20parliament%20is%20called%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20for%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20are%2029%20and%2035%2C%20respectively.%20According%20to%20the%20data%2C%20some%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20have%20a%20lower%20percentage%20of%20women%20representatives%20than%20India%20are%20Sri%20Lanka%20(5%25)%2C%20Qatar%20(4%25)%2C%20Oman%20(2%25)%20and%20Kuwait%20(3%25).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%2050%25%2C%20countries%20that%20have%20equal%20representation%20of%20men%20and%20women%20include%20New%20Zealand%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20The%20list%20is%20topped%20by%20Rwanda%2C%20with%2061%25%20of%20representatives%20in%20its%20lower%20house%20being%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tabled%20by%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies.%20The%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20about%2014%2C%20according%20to%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20government%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695117300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fgnlucpbo_parliament-lok-sabha-generic_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-bangladesh-pak-have-higher-percentage-of-women-in-lower-house-than-india-4403766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2