d%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat.%20Dulat%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20statement%20and%20expulsion%20are%20a%20good%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20deliberately%20leaving%20you%20to%20hear%20the%20interview%20to%20find%20out%20the%20answers%20to%20these%20issues.%20Watch%20the%20full%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8mzpTci1fUw%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695116701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19151307%2FKT-19-Sep.00_29_19_08.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fraw-modi-government-canada-karan-thapar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amarjit%20Singh%20Dulat%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20India%20is%20a%20liberal%20democracy%20and%20assassinating%20people%2C%20whether%20at%20home%20or%20abroad%2C%20is%20not%20something%20India%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20or%20security%20agencies%20have%20ever%20even%20contemplated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fraw-modi-government-canada-karan-thapar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kashyap%20on%20being%20taken%20for%20granted%20%26amp%3B%20misused%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695116304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103780840%2Cimgsize-28812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanurag-kashyap-on-being-taken-for-granted-and-misused-people-perceive-me-as-a-millionaire-ngo%2Farticleshow%2F103780859.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103780859.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERenowned%20filmmaker%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20has%20opened%20up%20a