th%20relatives%20and%20friends.%20But%20his%20stepmother%20and%20father%20continued%20spreading%20scandalous%20canards%20about%20him%2C%20forcing%20some%20of%20his%20close%20friends%20to%20snap%20ties%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saira%2C%20his%20aunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19101150%2FIMG_0232.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19101150%2FIMG_0232.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19101150%2FIMG_0232-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19101150%2FIMG_0232-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENagam%20is%20a%20village%20located%20some%2020%20kilometres%20from%20Kokernag%2C%20where%20the%20operation%20against%20militants%20is%20underway.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFarida%2C%20Uzair%E2%80%99s%20stepmother%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20the%20allegations%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20I%20took%20care%20of%20him%20in%20childhood%20and%20raised%20him%20like%20my%20own%20sons%2C%20I%20was%20always%20accused%20by%20his%20uncles%20of%20treating%20him%20badly%20and%20also%20held%20responsible%20for%20his%20fate.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20give%20my%20husband%20his%20share%20of%20property%20only%20because%20of%20Uzair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20he%20lived%20under%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20watch%2C%20the%20situation%20would%20not%20have%20come%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%20Bashir%20and%20Uzair%E2%80%99s%20brother%20are%20presently%20being%20questioned%20