ial%20liabilities%20of%20households%20rose%20sharply%20by%205.8%25%20of%20GDP%20compared%20with%203.8%25%20in%20FY22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20indicates%20that%20households%20have%20been%20largely%20borrowing%20to%20fulfil%20their%20consumption%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rate%20of%20increase%20in%20financial%20liabilities%20last%20fiscal%20(FY23)%20was%20the%20second%20highest%20since%20Independence%2C%20the%20newspaper%20noted.%20In%20FY07%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20increase%20was%20sharper%206.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20absolute%20terms%2C%20net%20household%20assets%20in%20FY21%20stood%20at%20Rs%2022.8%20trillion.%20In%20FY22%2C%20it%20dropped%20to%20Rs%2016.96%20trillion.%20It%20further%20fell%20to%20Rs%2013.76%20trillion%20in%20FY23.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20household%20debt%20has%20increased.%20%3Cem%3EFE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20stock%20of%20financial%20liabilities%2C%20household%20debt%20consequently%20remained%20sharply%20elevated%20at%2037.6%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20FY23%2C%20as%20against%2036.9%25%20in%20FY22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20these%20pressures%2C%20wages%20have%20not%20risen%20amid%20high%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFalling%20or%20stagnant%20wages%20coupled%20with%20high%20inflation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20of%20high%20inflation%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20significant%20growth%20in%20real%20wages%20at%20the%20all-India%20level%20over%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20healthcare%20and%20education%20is%20rising%2C%20most%20of%20which%20has%20to%20be%20borne%20privately.%20In%202021%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20medical%20inflation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fcost-of-treatment-doubles-in-5-years-as-medical-inflation-bites%2Farticleshow%2F102961777.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewas%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%2012%25%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20among%20all%20Asian%20countries.%20The%20cost%20of%20treatment%20has%20doubled%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fbanking-and-finance%2Feducation-inflation-tips-to-invest-for-children-education-8880375%2F%5C%22%3Eeducation%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20been%20significantly%20high%20at%2011-12%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20falling%20or%20stagnant%20household%20incomes%2C%20amid%20high%20inflation%2C%20is%20probably%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20subdued%20savings%20and%20higher%20borrowings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20RBI%20data%20on%20household%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20also%20raise%20worries%20about%20the%20immediate%20growth%20potential%20of%20the%20economy.%20The%20support%20to%20growth%20from%20private%20consumption%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20weaker%20than%20anticipated%2C%20even%20as%20a%20private%20capex%20cycle%20appears%20to%20be%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Gupta%2C%20economist%20at%20Motilal%20Oswal%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20FE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20weak%20income%20growth%20and%20falling%20financial%20savings%2C%20led%20by%20borrowings%2C%20is%20unsustainable.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20consumption%20growth%20is%20unsustainable.%20Whether%20it%20will%20be%20substituted%20by%20investments%20is%20not%20our%20base%20case%2C%20though%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695113433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16115416%2Frupee-g803a66102_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fhousehold-savings-fall-to-five-decade-low-in-fy23-debt-remains-sharply-elevated-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20indicates%20that%20households%20have%20been%20largely%20borrowing%20to%20fulfil%20their%20consumption%20needs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fhousehold-savings-fall-to-five-decade-low-in-fy23-debt-remains-sharply-elevated-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Former%20Foreign%20Minister%20Was%20Ousted%20Over%20His%20Affair%20In%20US%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20removed%20former%20Foreign%20Minister%20Qin%20Gang%20from%20the%20post%20after%20an%20investigation%20concluded%20he'd%20conducted%20an%20affair%20and%20fathered%20a%20child%20while%20serving%20as%20US%20ambassador%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%20Top%20officials%20were%20told%20in%20August%20that%20a%20Communist%20Party%20inquiry%20into%20Qin%20uncovered%20%26quot%3Blifestyle%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20newspaper%20reported%20Tuesday%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20situation%20that%20it%20didn't%20describe.%20That%20phrase%20usually%20means%20sexual%20misbehavior%20of%20some%20type%20in%20the%20parlance%20of%20Chinese%20officialdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20people%20said%20the%20affair%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20child%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20probe%2C%20with%20Qin's%20assistance%2C%20is%20now%20focusing%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20affair%20compromised%20national%20security.%20China%20is%20locked%20in%20an%20ideological%20battle%20with%20the%20US%2C%20its%20chief%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20rival%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20Beijing%20intensify%20a%20national%20security%20drive%20to%20shield%20it%20from%20foreign%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Ministry%20in%20Beijing%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Tuesday.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnot-found-chinas-ex-foreign-minister-is-gone-but-wait-for-explanation-goes-on-4257302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20stripped%20Qin%20from%20his%20ministerial%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20just%20seven%20months%20after%20he%20started%20the%20job%20-%20making%20his%20tenure%20the%20shortest%20in%20that%20role.%20No%20explanation%20was%20given%20for%20Qin's%20removal%20as%20his%20predecessor%20Wang%20Yi%20was%20reinstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20raised%20questions%20over%20President%20Xi%20Jinping's%20decision-making%20and%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20government%20running%20the%20world's%20No.%202%20economy.%20Those%20concerns%20are%20being%20rekindled%20by%20the%20current%20unexplained%20absence%20of%20Defense%20Minister%20Li%20Shangfu%2C%20amid%20media%20reports%20he's%20being%20probed%20for%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Communist%20Party's%20senior%20ranks%20are%20now%20being%20scrutinized%20for%20their%20dealings%20with%20foreigners%2C%20the%20insiders%20told%20the%20WSJ%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20top%20brass%20in%20China's%20military%20were%20also%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFew%20Chinese%20officials%20have%20risen%20as%20swiftly%20through%20the%20diplomatic%20ranks%20as%20Qin.%20His%20big%20break%20came%20in%202015%20when%20he%20was%20given%20oversight%20of%20protocol%20at%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%20That%20six-year%20stint%20saw%20him%20organize%20state%20visits%20of%20top%20leaders%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20likely%20in%20that%20role%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-qin-gang-scrubbed-from-foreign-ministry-website-after-dramatic-removal-4240336%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQin%20gained%20access%20to%20Xi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20pictured%20beside%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20then%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20Beijing%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Qin%20was%20sent%20to%20Washington%2C%20while%20he%20was%20still%20relatively%20unknown%20outside%20diplomatic%20circles%20or%20the%20Beijing%20press%20corps.%20He%20showed%20a%20flair%20for%20public%20relations%2C%20embracing%20American%20culture%20by%20openly%20attending%20a%20baseball%20game%20and%20riding%20in%20a%20Tesla%20Inc.%20with%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20moderate%20remarks%20on%20hot%20topics%2C%20arguing%20Beijing%20would've%20tried%20to%20stop%20Russia%20from%20invading%20Ukraine%20if%20it%20had%20known%20its%20plans%20and%20playing%20down%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20war%20with%20Taiwan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695113340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fdnsso0ao_qin-gang-reuters_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-former-foreign-minister-qin-gang-was-ousted-over-his-affair-in-us-report-4403558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20removed%20former%20Foreign%20Minister%20Qin%20Gang%20from%20the%20post%20after%20an%20investigation%20concluded%20he'd%20conducted%20an%20affair%20and%20fathered%20a%20child%20while%20serving%20as%20US%20ambassador%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-former-foreign-minister-qin-gang-was-ousted-over-his-affair-in-us-report-4403558%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-former-foreign-minister-qin-gang-was-ousted-over-his-affair-in-us-report-4403558%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-former-foreign-minister-qin-gang-was-ousted-over-his-affair-in-us-report-4403558%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Govt%20Under%20Fire%20for%20'Holding%20Back%20Narmada%20Waters%20for%20PM%20Modi's%20Birthday%20Causing%20Floods'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135716%2FThe-Wire-13.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20have%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20of%20holding%20back%20waters%20in%20the%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20Dam%20on%20the%20Narmada%20River%20for%20two%20days%20before%20releasing%20a%20huge%20volume%20%E2%80%93%2018%20lakh%20cusecs%20%E2%80%93%20all%20at%20once%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%2017%2C%20leading%20to%20floods%20in%20five%20districts%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20downstream%20Bharuch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20this%20was%20done%20to%20%E2%80%9Cplease%E2%80%9D%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20celebrated%20his%2073rd%20birthday%20that%20day.%20Calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cman-made%E2%80%9D%20disaster%2C%20they%20said%20the%20officials%20deliberately%20made%20the%20reservoir%20overflow%20and%20released%20water%20in%20one%20go%2C%20affecting%20lakhs%20of%20people%20and%20resulting%20in%20large-scale%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGujarat%20has%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days%20been%20receiving%20heavy%20rains%20across%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20Rivers%2C%20reservoirs%20and%20other%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20state%20are%20overflowing%20due%20to%20the%20continuous%20downpour.%20Rescue%20personnel%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%2C%20have%20been%20pressed%20into%20action%20in%20flood-affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2018%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Manish%20Doshi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fman-made-disaster-gujarat-bjp-govt-narmada-waters-modi-flood-congress-8945144%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20heavy%20rains%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20hourly%20monitoring%20of%20water%20levels%20in%20Narmada%20dam%2C%20the%20authorities%20did%20not%20release%20adequate%20amount%20of%20water%20on%20September%2015%20and%2016%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20dam%20to%20overflow%20on%20September%2017%20to%20make%20someone%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20negligence%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20quantum%20of%20water%20released%20thereafter%20was%20so%20big%20%E2%80%93%2018%20lakh%20cusecs%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20flooded%20towns%20and%20cities%20located%20downstream%20including%20Bharuch%2C%20Chanod%20and%20Karnali.%20This%20is%20a%20man-made%20flood.%20We%20demand%20all%20concerned%20officials%20be%20booked%20for%20criminal%20negligence%20and%20confiscate%20their%20property%20for%20paying%20compensation%20to%20the%20flood%20victims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20officials%20ignored%20data%20available%20from%20the%20agencies%20concerned%2C%20resulting%20in%20large-scale%20damage.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Meteorological%20Department%20observed%20exceptionally%20high%20district-wise%20rainfall%20for%20the%2024%20hours%20ending%2008-30%20hours%20on%20September%2016%2C%202023.%20Among%20the%20others%20are%20Khargaon%20(144.6%20mm)%2C%20Alirajpur%20(108.2%20mm)%2C%20Dewas%20(149.7%20mm)%2C%20Dhar%20(80.4%20mm)%2C%20Harda%20(205.2%20mm)%2C%20Jhabua%20(92.4%20mm)%2C%20Khandwa%20(147.6%20mm)%2C%20and%20Narmadapuram%20(131.7%20mm).%20CWC%20%5BCentral%20Water%20Commission%5D%20and%20SSP%20%5BSardar%20Sarovar%20Project%5D%20authorities%20receive%20hourly%20rainfall%20information%20in%20the%20watershed%2C%20thus%20they%20could%20have%20projected%20the%20flow%20and%20increased%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20the%20downstream%20river%20even%20before%20the%20IMD%20announced%20the%2024-hour%20figure%20at%2008-30%20hrs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F18%2Fgujarat-bjp-held-back-narmada-waters-on-pm-modis-birthday-creating-a-delugeallegescongress-2616079.html%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20further%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20on%20September%2014%2C%20the%20Burgi%20Dam%20gates%20on%20the%20Narmada%20were%20opened.%20The%20levels%20of%20the%20Narmada%E2%80%99s%20Indira%20Sagar%20and%20Omkareshwar%20dams%20had%20begun%20to%20increase%20by%20the%20late%20evening%20of%20September%2015.%20By%20late%20afternoon%2C%20both%20the%20Omkareshwar%20and%20Indira%20Sagar%20dams%20had%20reached%20their%20FRL%20(full%20reservoir%20level).%20This%20was%20yet%20another%20signal%20for%20SSP%20authorities%20to%20begin%20opening%20the%20SSP%20gates%20on%20September%2014%20and%2015%2C%20since%20the%20water%20discharged%20from%20the%20upstream%20dam%20was%20bound%20to%20reach%20the%20SSP.%20However%2C%20as%20of%2010%20am%20on%20September%2016%2C%20the%20SSP%20authorities%20had%20still%20not%20opened%20any%20gates%20from%20the%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20project%2C%20with%20solely%20River%20Bed%20releases.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20his%20party%20would%20be%20writing%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cerring%E2%80%9D%20officials.%20%E2%80%9CHad%20%5Bthey%5D%20acted%20in%20time%2C%20the%20flood%20waters%20from%20Narmada%20could%20have%20been%20easily%20diverted%20to%20Saurashtra%20where%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20for%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20state%20unit%20president%20Shaktisinh%20Gohil%20said%20the%20floods%20were%20a%20result%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdrama%E2%80%9D%20enacted%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20state%20officials%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20birthday.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20sorrow%20that%20over%2017%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20were%20released%20from%20the%20Narmada%20Dam%20in%20Bharuch%20on%20one%20day.%20In%20total%2C%2018.2%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20were%20released%20simultaneously%2C%20leading%20to%20waterlogging%20in%20low-lying%20areas%20of%20Bharuch.%20Water%20rushed%20in%20up%20to%20the%20second%20stories%20of%20buildings%2C%20causing%20significant%20losses%20and%20destroying%20farms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeshgujarat.com%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Fcongress-blames-gujarat-govt-for-bharuch-flood-govt-refutes-the-allegations%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20had%20the%20water%20been%20released%20in%20smaller%20instalments%2C%20things%20would%20have%20been%20different%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20because%20September%2017%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20birthday%2C%20and%20for%20that%20occasion%2C%20the%20dam%20was%20filled%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20went%20there%20to%20perform%20a%20pooja.%20To%20carry%20out%20this%20drama%2C%20the%20water%2C%20which%20had%20been%20rising%20since%20last%20week%2C%20was%20not%20released%2C%20and%20the%20turbines%20were%20shut%20down.%20Instead%2C%20if%20the%20water%20had%20been%20released%20in%20smaller%20installments%2C%20this%20destruction%20would%20not%20have%20occurred%2C%20and%20people%20would%20not%20have%20suffered%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20underlining%20that%20Modi%20may%20not%20have%20information%20about%20such%20a%20thing%20happening%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20government%20should%20not%20have%20undertaken%20such%20a%20gimmick%20to%20impress%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20putting%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20danger.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20chief%20minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20had%20flown%20to%20Kevadiya%2C%20the%20site%20of%20the%20dam%2C%20on%20Sunday%20morning%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CNarmada%20Jal%20Na%20Vadhamana%E2%80%9D%20or%20to%20welcome%20the%20Narmada%20waters.%20The%20day%20also%20marked%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2073rd%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPal%20Ambaliya%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Kisan%20Congress%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20wing%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20(GPCC)%2C%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Sarovar%20dam%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20to%20overflow%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20thing%20had%20happened.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20predicted%20last%20year%2015%20days%20in%20advance%20that%20Narmada%20dam%20would%20overflow%20on%20September%2017%20only%20and%20my%20prediction%20was%20proven%20right%E2%80%A6%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20this%20year%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fman-made-disaster-gujarat-bjp-govt-narmada-waters-modi-flood-congress-8945144%2F%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20neighbouring%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20officials%20of%20releasing%209.45%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Indirasagar%20Dam%20in%20their%20state%20to%20make%20the%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20overflow%20on%20September%2017.%20The%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20too.%20Narmada%20river%20flows%20through%20both%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20and%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20celebrate%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20and%20present%20him%20as%20a%20larger-than-life%20%E2%80%98Messiah%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20some%20bunch%20of%20fools%20in%20the%20BJP%20government%20decided%20to%20open%20the%20floodgates%20of%20Narmada%20Dam%20yesterday%20(without%20any%20prior%20warning%20in%20nearby%20areas)%2C%20and%20released%2018%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20at%20once%20leading%20to%20misery%20and%20devastation%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%2C%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETo%20celebrate%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20and%20present%20him%20as%20a%20larger%20than%20life%20%E2%80%98Messiah%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20some%20bunch%20of%20fools%20in%20the%20BJP%20government%20decided%20to%20open%20the%20floodgates%20of%20Narmada%20Dam%20yesterday%20(without%20any%20prior%20warning%20in%20nearby%20areas)%2C%20and%20released%2018%20lakh%20cusecs%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuJYfsY0rgN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuJYfsY0rgN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20(%40jigneshmevani80)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjigneshmevani80%2Fstatus%2F1703749596063908144%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cman-made%20disaster%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20further%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20could%20easily%20have%20been%20released%20in%20a%20phase%20to%20these%20regions%20few%20days%20prior%20as%20a%20red%20alert%20was%20already%20issued%20and%20there%20was%20going%20to%20be%20more%20water%20in%20the%20dam.%20But%20does%20that%20count%20for%20a%20birthday%20celebration%3F%20No%20right%3F%20-They%20waited%20for%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20to%20release%20the%20water.%20Hence%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20natural%20flood%20but%20a%20man-made%20disaster%20to%20celebrate%20the%20%E2%80%98Messiah%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChronology%20of%20Gujarat%20floods%20!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Indirasagar%20Dam%20released%209.45%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20into%20Narmada%2C%20days%20before%20PM%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20so%20that%20the%20Narmada%20Dam%20reservoir%20reaches%20maximum%20water%20levels%20before%20PM