_origin%3DBBCHindi%26at_bbc_team%3Deditorial%26at_medium%3Dsocial%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20around%202%2C800%20employees%20of%20the%20HEC%20claim%20that%20have%20not%20received%20their%20salaries%20for%20the%20past%2018%20months.%20Among%20them%20is%20Mr%20Uprariya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMeet%20Deepak%20Kumar%20Uprariya%20who%20sells%20Tea%20%26amp%3B%20Idli%20in%20Ranchi.%20He%20is%20a%20Technician%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20building%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-3%20launchpad.%20For%20the%20last%2018%20months%2C%20he%20has%20not%20received%20any%20salary.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20die%20of%20hunger%2C%20I%20opened%20an%20Idli%20shop%26quot%3B%20(BBC%20Reports)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcHqytJvtfj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcHqytJvtfj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Cow%20Momma%20(%40Cow__Momma)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCow__Momma%2Fstatus%2F1703453373310042379%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20Mr%20Uprariya%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20selling%20idlis%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20He%20has%20been%20managing%20his%20shop%20and%20office%20work%20together.%20The%20technician%20sells%20idlis%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20goes%20to%20the%20office%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20he%20sells%20idlis%20again%20before%20heading%20back%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20situation%2C%20Mr%20Uprariya%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20I%20managed%20my%20house%20with%20a%20credit%20card.%20I%20got%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20I%20was%20declared%20a%20defaulter.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20started%20running%20the%20house%20by%20taking%20money%20from%20relatives.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20I%20have%20taken%20a%20loan%20of%20four%20lakh%20rupees.%20As%20I%20have%20not%20returned%20the%20money%20to%20anyone%2C%20now%20people%20have%20stopped%20lending.%20Then%20I%20mortgaged%20my%20wife's%20jewellery%20and%20ran%20the%20house%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20technician%20said%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20sell%20idlis%20when%20he%20felt%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Btime%20of%20starvation%26quot%3B%20had%20come%20upon%20him.%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20makes%20good%20idlis.%20I%20get%20300%20to%20400%20rupees%20every%20day%20by%20selling%20them.%20I%20make%20a%20profit%20of%2050-100%20rupees.%20I%20am%20running%20my%20house%20on%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-quits-company-after-19-years-4402204%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20Chief%20Product%20Officer%20Panos%20Panay%20Quits%20Company%20After%2019%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mr%20Upraria%20hails%20from%20the%20Harda%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20a%20private%20company%20and%20joined%20HEC%20on%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%208%2C000.%20Being%20a%20government%20company%2C%20he%20had%20hoped%20that%20his%20future%20would%20be%20bright%20but%20things%20did%20not%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20two%20daughters.%20Both%20go%20to%20school.%20This%20year%20I%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20pay%20their%20school%20fees%20yet.%20Daily%20notices%20are%20being%20sent%20by%20the%20school.%20Even%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20teachers%20ask%20who%20are%20the%20children%20of%20parents%20working%20in%20HEC%20to%20stand%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20children%20are%20humiliated%20after%20this.%20My%20daughters%20come%20home%20crying.%20It%20breaks%20my%20heart%20to%20see%20them%20cry.%20But%20I%20don't%20cry%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Upraria%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20situation%20is%20not%20only%20for%20Deepak%20Upararia.%20Like%20him%2C%20some%20other%20people%20associated%20with%20HEC%20are%20also%20earning%20their%20livelihood%20by%20doing%20similar%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695111060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fhrpaqfko_hec-employee-deepak-kumar-uprariya_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftechnician-who-helped-build-chandrayaan-3-launchpad-now-selling-idlis-read-his-story-4403414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepak%20Kumar%20Uprariya%2C%20a%20technician%20in%20HEC%20(Heavy%20Engineering%20Corporation%20Limited)%20who%20worked%20for%20building%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-3%20launchpad%2C%20has%20been%20selling%20idlis%20at%20a%20roadside%20stall%20in%20Ranchi%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftechnician-who-helped-build-chandrayaan-3-launchpad-now-selling-idlis-read-his-story-4403414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftechnician-who-helped-build-chandrayaan-3-launchpad-now-selling-idlis-read-his-story-4403414%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftechnician-who-helped-build-chandrayaan-3-launchpad-now-selling-idlis-read-his-story-4403414%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Bihar%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Ignored%20the%20Real%20Issues%20to%20Focus%20on%20Communal%20Polarisation%20Agenda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19124219%2FF6JjKpKbAAA6xPD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Attack%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esanatan%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98infiltration%20(of%20Muslims%20from%20Bangladesh)%E2%80%99%2C%20cancellation%20of%20holidays%20for%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20and%20Janmashtami%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98appeasement%20(of%20minorities)%E2%80%99%20constituted%20the%20central%20themes%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech%20at%20Jhanjharpur%20in%20Bihar%20on%20September%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Nitish%20Kumar%20dumped%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20%E2%80%93%20now%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20%E2%80%93%20Shah%20has%20visited%20Bihar%20four%20times.%20He%20has%20invariably%20addressed%20public%20meetings%20in%20Seemanchal-Purnia%20and%20Kishenganj%20bordering%20north%20Bengal%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20Mithila%20regions%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20north-east%20Bihar%20with%20a%20relatively%20denser%20concentration%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJhanjharpur%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Mithila%20region%2C%20known%20for%20Madhubani%20paintings%2C%20saint-poet%20Vidyapati%E2%80%99s%20songs%2C%20the%20religious%20discourse%20between%20Aadi%20Shankaracharya%20and%20Mandan%20Mishra%2C%20the%20age-old%20culture%20of%20eating%20%3Cem%3Epaan-maachh-makhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(betel%20leaves%2C%20fish%20and%20lotus%20seeds)%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20communal%20harmony.%20The%20regions%20have%20never%20witnessed%20large-scale%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20past.%20But%20Shah%20showed%20little%20interest%20in%20what%20had%20kept%20the%20people%20strung%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20humiliating%20sanatan%20dharma.%20The%20Nitish%20government%20has%20specifically%20targeted%20Hindu%20festivals%20by%20cancelling%20holidays%20for%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20and%20Janmashtami%20%5Bthe%20holidays%20had%20been%20restored%20when%20Shah%20spoke%5D.%20The%20infiltration%20%5Bof%20Muslims%20from%20Bangladesh%5D%20will%20increase%20manifold%20if%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024%20and%20the%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20replace%20the%20Nitish%20government%20in%202025%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20his%20government%20had%20built%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20at%20Darbhanga%2C%20inviting%20severe%20criticism%20for%20what%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Tejaswhi%20Yadav%2C%20termed%20%E2%80%9Cwhite%20lies%E2%80%9D.%20There%20is%20no%20AIIMS%20at%20Darbhanga.%20Shah%20shifted%20the%20blame%20on%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20for%20allotting%20a%20%E2%80%9Clow%20lying%20field%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%20fervently%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20bring%20Modi%20back%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term%20in%202024%20but%20escaped%20from%20mentioning%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20promises%20to%20Bihar%2C%20including%20a%20special%20package%20of%20Rs%20125%20lakh%20crore%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20announced%20at%20his%20election%20meeting%20at%20Arra%20ahead%20of%20the%202015%20assembly%20polls.%20Among%20many%20of%20his%20lofty%20promises%20specific%20to%20Bihar%2C%20Modi%20had%20also%20promised%20to%20make%20the%20fruits-%20and%20vegetables-producing%20Vaishali%20region%20the%20%E2%80%9Chub%20of%20the%20food%20processing%20industry%E2%80%9D%20ahead%20of%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20the%20drought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%20focused%20only%20on%20divisive%20issues%2C%20ignoring%20the%20drought%20that%20is%20looming%20large%20on%20the%20state%20due%20to%20inadequate%20rainfall%20this%20monsoon%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20notice%20of%20what%20they%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitish%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20reporters%E2%80%99%20questions%20about%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20knowledge%20whatsoever%20about%20the%20development%20work%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20have%20no%20knowledge%20about%20the%20country%20either.%20They%20brazenly%20and%20relentlessly%20speak%20in%20insensible%20manners%20which%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20attention%20to.%E2%80%9D%20He%20suggested%20the%20journalists%20focus%20on%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%20preoccupied%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20drought.%20Nitish%20has%20continuously%20been%20reviewing%20the%20situation%2C%20particularly%20in%20south%20Bihar%20with%20the%20hills%20devoid%20of%20vegetation%20and%20stony%20lands%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20central%20Bihar%20with%20little%20water%20bodies.%20He%20has%20announced%20subsidies%20on%20diesel%20and%20has%20deliberated%20on%20the%20issue%20with%20officials%20and%20his%20ministers%20concerned%20several%20times%20of%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Union%20government%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20drought%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20Be%20it%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20or%20other%20prime%20ministers%20in%20the%20past%2C%20they%20always%20sent%20the%20team%20of%20Central%20officials%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20arising%20out%20of%20droughts%20and%20floods%20in%20the%20states%20and%20helped%20them%20accordingly.%20But%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20who%20holds%20as%20important%20a%20portfolio%20as%20home%20%E2%80%93%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20it%20necessary%20to%20even%20mention%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDivisive%20agenda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmit%20Shah%20lacks%20in%20the%20basic%20manners%20and%20decency%20of%20how%20a%20Union%20home%20minister%20should%20speak%20and%20act.%20Incidentally%2C%20he%20comes%20from%20the%20state%20of%20Sardar%20Vallabhai%20Patel%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20Union%20home%20minister%20of%20India.%20But%20he%20shamelessly%20talks%20in%20terms%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20this%20multi-cultural%20and%20diverse%20country%20nursed%20with%20the%20life-blood%20of%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20veteran%20socialist%20leader%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20national%20vice-president%20Shivanand%20Tiwary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETiwary%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20(Bihar)%20is%20the%20land%20of%20Gandhi%20ji%20and%20JP.%20The%20communal%20operations%20of%20Shah%20and%20Modi%20won%E2%80%99t%20work%20here.%20But%20they%20(Modi%20and%20Shah)%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20anything%20else%20other%20than%20dividing%20society%20and%20polarising%20the%20electorate%20on%20communal%20lines%20to%20win%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RJD%20leader%20was%20not%20wide%20off%20the%20mark.%20Political%20observers%20believe%20that%20Shah%20might%20be%20trying%20to%20experiment%20with%20a%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots-like%20situation%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Mithila%20and%20Seemanchal%20regions%2C%20which%20are%20similar%20to%20Muzaffarnagar%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20minority%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuzaffarnagar%20had%20witnessed%20large-scale%20communal%20conflagration%20ahead%20of%20the%202014%20elections.%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20the%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20BJP%20then%20%E2%80%93%20harnessed%20the%20violence%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20to%20their%20electoral%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20first%20place%20that%20Shah%20visited%20ahead%20of%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20Kairana.%20He%20had%20selectively%20gone%20only%20at%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%99%20doors%2C%20ignoring%20the%20minorities%20who%20were%20the%20bigger%20victims%20of%20the%20riots.%20Significantly%2C%20Shah%20had%20tried%20to%20stoke%20the%20communal%20divide%20in%20Muzzaffarnagar%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20stir%20had%20bridged%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20and%20they%20were%20opposing%20the%20three%20later-withdrawn%20farm%20bills%20in%20a%20collective%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20be%20hard%20to%20replicate%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20Kairana%20in%20Mithila%20and%20Seemanchal%20which%20have%20been%20the%20cradle%20of%20communal%20amity%20and%20peace%20for%20centuries.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20tactics%20won%E2%80%99t%20work%20in%20Mithila%20and%20Seemanchal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdul%20Bari%20Siddiqui%2C%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20national%20general%20secretary%20who%20has%20represented%20Mithila%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20assembly%20several%20times%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695111027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19124219%2FF6JjKpKbAAA6xPD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bihar-amit-shah-ignored-the-real-issues-to-focus-on-communal-polarisation-agenda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20the%20state%20is%20facing%20a%20looming%20drought%20due%20to%20inadequate%20rainfall%20this%20monsoon%2C%20Amit%20Shah's%20speech%20only%20raised%20polarising%20issues%20like%20sanatan%20dharma%2C%20infiltration%20and%20minority%20'appeasement'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bihar-amit-shah-ignored-the-real-issues-to-focus-on-communal-polarisation-agenda%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aaliyah%20Qureishi%20on%20dancing%20with%20SRK%20in%20Jawan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695109939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.c