%3E%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20Queensland%20state%20police%20have%20released%20documents%20of%20their%20investigation%20into%20graffiti%20that%20defaced%20a%20temple%E2%80%99s%20outer%20wall%20in%20Brisbane.%20The%20papers%20suggest%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20close%20this%20matter%20after%20getting%20no%20more%20leads%20from%20the%20complainants%20and%20there%20seems%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20hand%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20anti-Modi%20graffiti%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdone%20on%20the%20night%20of%20March%203%20but%20blamed%20on%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Foz-police-see-hindu-hand-in-temple-graffiti-advise-closure%2Farticleshow%2F103744961.cms%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20police%20said%20that%20they%20have%20no%20suspects%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20investigators%20proposed%20a%20theory%20that%20the%20Hindus%20defaced%20their%20own%20temple%20after%20shutting%20off%20the%20key%20CCTV%20cameras%20purposely%20and%20the%20serial%20offender%20who%20had%20done%20similar%20mischief%20in%20Victoria%20had%20then%20sneaked%20into%20Brisbane%E2%80%99s%20Sikh%20rally%20of%20March%204.%20Three%20more%20Australian%20temples%20have%20been%20defaced%20since%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20cites%20documents%20made%20available%20by%20the%20Australian%20police%20in%20response%20to%20a%20right%20to%20information%20query.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Australian%20police%20released%20five%20full%20and%20seven%20partial%20investigation%20documents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjindaginama.com%2Fpress-release%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20Sikh%20activist%20and%20author%20Bhabishan%20Singh%20Goraya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20had%20alleged%20that%20Sikhs%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20vandalism%20without%20inquiry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20also%20quotes%20from%20a%20supplementary%20report%20saying%20that%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20complainants%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20give%20us%20any%20CCTV%20footage%E2%80%A6%20someone%20with%20no%20ties%20to%20the%20temple%E2%80%A6%20may%20have%20been%20involved%20to%20encourage%20dissent%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs.%20The%20inquiry%E2%80%A6%20did%20not%20show%20that%20it%20was%20in%20the%20area%20of%20offence%20during%20the%20time%20it%20occurred.%20All%20cameras%20went%20offline%20at%20about%206.30pm%20on%20March%203%20shortly%20after%20being%20installed.%20It%20could%20be%20an%20installation%20fault%20or%20done%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20facilitating%20the%20offence%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20in%20all%20capital%20letters%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20CCTV%20may%20have%20been%20purposely%20shut%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fworld%2Fstory%2Fhindu-temple-vandalised-walls-defaced-with-graffiti-in-australias-brisbane-2342473-2023-03-04%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20temple%2C%20situated%20in%20Burbank%2C%20a%20suburb%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Brisbane%2C%20was%20vandalised%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20walls%20defaced%20with%20graffiti%E2%80%9D%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20This%20was%20said%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fourth%20such%20incident%20involving%20a%20temple%20in%20Australia%20in%20two%20months%E2%80%9D.%20The%20vandalism%20was%20noticed%20when%20devotees%20came%20for%20their%20morning%20prayers%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20wrote%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20when%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20Australia%20in%20May%2C%20in%20a%20somewhat%20unusual%20move%2C%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20vandalism%20of%20Hindu%20temples%E2%80%9D.%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-anthony-albanese-hindu-temples-vandalism-australia-101684896781300.html%5C%22%3EAnthony%20Albanese%20told%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20gave%20him%20(Modi)%20the%20assurance%20Australia%20is%20a%20country%20that%20respects%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith%E2%80%A6%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20the%20sort%20of%20extreme%20actions%20and%20attacks%20we%20have%20seen%20on%20religious%20temples%2C%20be%20they%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20synagogues%2C%20or%20churches.%20This%20has%20no%20place%20in%20Australia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695109855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19125030%2FFqWlB5qX0AI6ZVK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Faustralia-documents-released-by-police-point-to-hindu-hand-in-temple-wall-defacement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Australian%20police%20released%20five%20full%20and%20seven%20partial%20investigation%20documents%20to%20Sikh%20activist%20and%20author%20Bhabishan%20Singh%20Goraya%2C%20who%20had%20alleged%20that%20%E2%80%9CSikhs%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20vandalism%20without%20inquiry.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Faustralia-documents-released-by-police-point-to-hindu-hand-in-temple-wall-defacement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Marines%20Orders%20All%20Aircraft%20To%20Be%20Grounded%20After%20F-35%20Disappearance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Eric%20Smith%2C%20the%20acting%20commandant%20of%20the%20US%20Marines%2C%20has%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20ground%20all%20Marine%20Corps%20aircraft%2C%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20United%20States%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20decision%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20mysterious%20disappearance%20of%20a%20stealth%20F-35%20jet%20in%20South%20Carolina.%20While%20Marine%20aircraft%20currently%20deployed%20abroad%20or%20those%20with%20imminent%20missions%20have%20the%20option%20to%20br