schedule.%20He%20woke%20up%20at%204%20am%20to%20help%20his%20parents%20at%20their%20snack%2Ftea%20shop.%20After%20returning%20from%20college%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20the%20shop%20till%2011%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20the%20southernmost%20part%20of%20India%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%20And%20he%20succeeded%20in%20his%20goals.%20Today%2C%20he%20lives%20in%20a%202%2C000-square-foot%2C%20four-bedroom%20house.%20He%20also%20supported%20his%20three%20younger%20siblings%E2%80%99%20education%20and%20marriage%2C%20making%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20lives%20comfortable.%20He%20credits%20all%20his%20achievements%20to%20his%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20made%20sure%20that%20he%20gave%20all%20of%20us%20a%20good%20education.%20He%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20educate%20us%20and%20managed%20to%20pay%20all%20our%20fees%20by%20borrowing%20money%20and%20mortgaging%20jewellery.%20Three%20of%20my%20siblings%20are%20postgraduates%20and%20one%20has%20completed%20her%20doctorate.%20All%20of%20us%20are%20in%20good%20positions%20thanks%20to%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20getting%20us%20educated%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20humble%20beginnings%20to%20deputy%20director%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330245%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20Nellayapan%20had%20just%20completed%20an%20MSc%20in%20physics.%20His%20older%20sister%20was%20getting%20married%2C%20for%20which%20his%20parents%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20tea%2Fsnack%20stall%2C%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20time%20before%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20People%20refused%20to%20lend%20money.%20My%20parents%20managed%20the%20required%20money%20with%20great%20difficulty.%20Till%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20the%20moneylenders%20kept%20us%20hanging.%20I%20felt%20so%20insulted.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20resolved%20to%20achieve%20something%20big%20in%20life%2C%20so%20my%20parents%20would%20never%20have%20to%20face%20such%20a%20situation%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%E2%80%99s%20college%20senior%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20apprised%20him%20about%20the%20opportunities%20there.%20And%20the%20then%2023-year-old%20left%20for%20Nagaland%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket%20and%20big%20dreams%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20four%20days%20to%20reach%20Nagaland.%20My%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20train%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%20had%20to%20pawn%20her%20last%20piece%20of%20jewellery%20%E2%80%94%20her%20nose%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20which%20got%20us%20Rs%202%2C000.%20I%20remember%20the%20bank%20manager%E2%80%99s%20expression%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20nose%20ring%2C%20knowing%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20I%20felt%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20the%20amount%20helped%20him%20with%20food%20and%20lodging%20for%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201991%2C%20he%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20private%20school%20teacher%20in%20Nagaland%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month.%20He%20shares%20that%20this%20money%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20cover%20his%20expenses%20as%20he%20sent%20some%20money%20back%20home%20too.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%20700%20per%20month%20for%20electricity%20and%20rent.%20How%20could%20I%20survive%20on%20just%20Rs%20300%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20taking%20tuition%20for%20school%20students%20to%20supplement%20my%20income.%20I%20used%20to%20tutor%20from%206%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20then%20attend%20school%20until%204%20pm%2C%20and%20return%20to%20tutor%20again%20until%206%20pm.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20managed%20for%20the%20first%20six%20years%20in%20private%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20Nagaland%20was%20facing%20insurgency%20issues.%20But%20the%20teacher%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20hinder%20his%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Nellayapan%20got%20a%20job%20as%20a%20postgraduate%20teacher%20in%20physics%20at%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Dimapur.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20got%20married%20and%20remembers%20how%20they%20then%20put%20an%20asbestos%20roof%20on%20their%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20burden%20of%20responsibility%20is%20often%20a%20blessing.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20school%20principal%20in%202012%20and%20continued%20working%20there%20till%202017.%20Then%2C%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20deputy%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20trailblazer%20in%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B's%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20of%20Nellayapan%E2%80%99s%20siblings%20are%20well-educated%20due%20to%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20efforts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID%20hit%20the%20nation%2C%20Nagaland%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20states%20to%20embrace%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20even%20recognised%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Co-operation%20and%20Development%20Education%20(OECD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202020%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20rolled%20out%20a%20tele%2Fonline%20education%20programme%20through%20which%20education%20was%20offered%20through%20TV%20(Doordarshan%2C%20Kohima)%20and%20radio%20(All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Kohima).%20In%20May%202020%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20educational%20content%20through%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20programme%20was%20led%20by%20C%20Shanavas%20%E2%80%94%20principal%20director%20of%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20supported%20by%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHeartiest%20congratulations%20to%20the%20awardees%20of%20Governor's%20Gold%20Medal%20and%20Governor's%20Commendation%20Certificate%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F74th_IndependenceDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation%20certificate%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20IAS%20officers%20like%20Shanavas%20was%20also%20a%20big%20motivation%20for%20Nellayapan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20many%20IAS%20officers.%20They%20are%20an%20inspiration%20for%20me%20and%20I%20wish%20to%20work%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20physics%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20his%20work%20and%20efforts%20towards%20improving%20education%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Nellayapan%20was%20made%20the%20OSD%20to%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Nagaland%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20here%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one%20for%20him%2C%20he%20shares.%20He%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20He%20credits%20his%20wife%20for%20being%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20his%20success.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20is%20my%20rock.%20She%20supported%20me%20since%20the%20day%20we%20got%20married.%20She%20also%20helped%20my%20younger%20sister%20get%20married.%20Today%2C%20my%20wife%20is%20a%20successful%20executive%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20children%20moved%20to%20Trivandrum%20because%20of%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20job.%20He%20proudly%20mentions%20that%20his%20son%20is%20now%20a%20doctor%2C%20and%20his%20daughter%20is%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReminiscing%20the%20past%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20concentrate%20only%20on%20work%20because%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20when%20I%20came%20here.%20I%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20siblings%20studied%20well%20and%20my%20parents%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20borrow%20money.%20Poverty%20and%20responsibility%20guided%20me%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%20has%20a%20message%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306810%2Fthis-heartwarming-story-of-determination-and-resilience-started-with-a-simple-no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20You%20might%20get%20the%20reward%20late%2C%20but%20keep%20at%20it.%20Hustle%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%20with%20focus.%20You%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20your%20efforts.%20Just%20work%20hard%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20mind%20get%20diverted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20many%20people%20helped%20his%20father%20with%20the%20loans.%20Even%20though%20his%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20his%20assistance%20now%2C%20this%20government%20officer%20is%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Today%2C%20he%20supports%20six%20students%20in%20their%20education.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20has%20blessed%20me%3B%20I%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20help%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd-ilibrary.org%2Fsites%2F61d5c87b-en%2Findex.html%3FitemId%3D%2Fcontent%2Fcomponent%2F61d5c87b-en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOECD%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20crushing%20poverty%20in%20a%20one-room%20house%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Kanniyakumari.%20Exemplifying%20the%20power%20of%20education%2C%20his%20inspiring%20story%20has%20won%20the%20Internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20expels%20Canadian%20diplomat%20amid%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-hardeep-singh-nijjar_6290069.jpg%3F20230919065647%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20expelled%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20amid%20an%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20leader%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A135%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20the%20Rishi%20Means%20to%20Hindutva%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19104342%2FF5p3YxSWsAA3PNf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20evoked%20myriad%20comments.%20Modi%20bhakts%20went%20gaga%20over%20Rishi%20being%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20and%20paying%20obeisance%20at%20Akshardham%20temple%2C%20while%20the%20British%20media%20and%20parliamentarians%20took%20this%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20accommodative%20and%20large-hearted%20British%20system.%20In%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20comment%20by%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20days%20Arif%2C%20after%20splitting%20with%20V.P.%20Singh%20post-Mandal%2C%20had%20finally%20made%20it%20to%20the%2012th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20led%20by%20Mayawati.%20The%20BJP%20had%20just%20come%20to%20power%20on%20the%20back%20of%20its%20militant%20Hindutva%20sloganeering%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMandir%20wahin%20banayenge%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20a%20subtle%20yet%20not%20so%20blas%C3%A9%20anti-Muslim%20campaign.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20undercurrent%20was%20pretty%20evident%20even%20then.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20some%20journalist%20friends%2C%20Arif%20debunked%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20Muslims%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20Muslims%20be%20any%20threat%20to%20this%20government%3F%20No%20Muslim%20can%20ever%20aspire%20to%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20true%2C%20though%20I%20doubt%20Arif%2C%20in%20his%20new%20saffron%20avatar%2C%20would%20like%20to%20be%20reminded%20of%20that%20comment%20anymore!%20But%20his%20prognosis%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20truer%20than%20probably%20even%20he%20believed%20then.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20much%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Ganges%20since%20that%20short-lived%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20lasted%20barely%2013%20months%2C%20as%20we%20approach%20the%20end%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20having%20reinvented%20himself%20as%20the%20presiding%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epujari%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Maa%20Ganga.%20To%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20credit%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim%20members%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20rose%20to%20a%20record%2034%20in%20the%2014the%20Lok%20Sabha%C2%A0%20(2004-09)%20dwindled%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20watchful%20eyes%20to%20a%20record%20low%20of%2022%20in%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20More%20pertinent%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Varanasi%20as%20his%20electoral%20Hindutva%20battlefield%20virtually%20wiped%20out%20Muslim%20representation%20from%20UP%2C%20which%20sends%2080%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20In%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20was%20elected%20from%20UP.%20Later%2C%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20sent%20up%20Begum%20Tabassum%20Hasan%20from%20its%20pocket%20borough%20of%20Kairana%20in%20May%202018%2C%20with%20exactly%20a%20year%20left%20for%20the%20term%20of%20that%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20end.%20And%20in%20the%2017th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20BJP%20recaptured%20that%20seat%20for%20their%20candidate%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Choudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20after%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20soon%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi%20became%20PM%2C%20the%20local%20general%20merchant%20would%20tell%20my%20mother%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAur%20do%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ko%20vote%2C%20jao%20poochho%20Indira%20Gandhi%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Go%20and%20ask%20Indira%20Gandhi%20whom%20you%20voted%20for)%E2%80%9D%20He%20presumed%20correctly%20that%20my%20mother%2C%20a%20Muslim%20government%20school%20teacher%20living%20in%20Timarpur%20Babu%20colony%2C%20would%20have%20voted%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Even%20way%20back%20in%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20the%20Sanghis%20held%20Muslims%20responsible%20for%20their%20inability%20to%20rule%20India.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20their%20ultimate%20ambition%20was%20to%20make%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETill%20the%2012th%20and%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20captured%20power%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20in%20coalition%20with%20other%20%E2%80%9Csecular%E2%80%9D%20parties%2C%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20dream%20of%20jettisoning%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20did%20not%20succeed.%20There%20were%2027%20Muslim%20MPs%20in%20the%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20with%20six%20from%20UP%2C%20six%20from%20West%20Bengal%20and%20five%20from%20Bihar.%20This%20was%20considerably%20higher%20than%20in%20the%2011th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20left-secular%20United%20Front%20(UF)%20government%20with%20merely%2024%20Muslim%20members%2C%20including%20just%20four%20from%20UP%20and%20three%20from%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20an%20even%20bigger%20disappointment%20for%20Sangh%20supporters%20of%20the%20Vajpayee-Advani-led%20NDA.%20That%20Lok%20Sabha%20threw%20up%2028%20Muslim%20members%20with%20seven%20from%20UP.%20Some%20consolation%3A%20there%20were%20only%20two%20from%20Bihar.%20But%20then%20Karnataka%20sent%20up%20two%20Muslims%20and%20even%20Maharashtra%20sent%20one%20to%20the%2013th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2014th%20Lok%20Sabha%20of%20the%20UPA%2C%20led%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20Catholic%20by%20birth%2C%20and%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Sikh%20PM%2C%20sent%20real%20shock%20waves%20among%20pseudo-nationalists.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Muslim%20representation%20touched%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%2034%2C%20with%20nine%20MPs%20from%20UP%20and%20six%20from%20undivided%20Bihar%2C%20including%20one%20from%20the%20new%20state%20of%20Jharkhand.%20Karnataka%20sent%20up%20one%2C%20so%20did%20Maharashtra%20and%20even%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20results%20of%20the%2015th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20were%20not%20so%20bad%2C%20with%2025%20Muslim%20MPs%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20those%20for%20whom%20Muslims%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctermites%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20rid%20from%20Bharat%20Desh%E2%80%99%20body%20politic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Modi%2C%20the%20Sangh%20dream%20finally%20came%20true%2C%20with%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20MP%20from%20UP%20and%20none%20from%20Karnataka%20or%20Maharashtra%2C%20forget%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20That%20is%20why%20when%20Modi%20won%20in%20May%2C%202014%2C%20the%20then%20international%20president%20of%20the%20VHP%20Ashok%20Singhal%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20finally%20gained%20freedom%20after%201%2C000%20years%E2%80%9D.%20Modi%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20refrain%2C%20even%20in%20his%20public%20speeches%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20there%20is%20reason%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20to%20celebrate%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20who%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconquered%E2%80%9D%20Britain.%20But%20they%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20formally%20Christian%20but%20liberal%20UK%20has%20received%20with%20open%20arms%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20as%20their%20PM.%20Forget%20about%20Muslims%2C%20remember%20how%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20and%20Uma%20Bharti%20announced%20after%C2%A0the%20UPA%20won%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202004%20%2C%20that%20they%20would%20shave%20their%20heads%20and%20sleep%20like%20Kaikeyi%20on%20the%20floor%20if%20Sonia%20ever%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20Never%20mind%20whom%20the%20people%20had%20voted%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19104342%2FF5p3YxSWsAA3PNf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-the-rishi-means-to-hindutva%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yes%2C%20there%20is%20reason%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20to%20celebrate%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20who%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconquered%E2%80%9D%20Britain.%20But%20th