22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66850943.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66850943.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP-AIADMK%20Row%20Intensifies%2C%20With%20AIADMK%20Saying%20There%20Is%20'No%20Alliance%20as%20of%20Now'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19093725%2FF6C-h8_aMAAx7mN.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20is%20not%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20and%20any%20such%20decisions%20will%20be%20taken%20during%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20alliance%20with%20AIADMK.%20We%20will%20decide%20about%20the%20alliance%20during%20the%20elections%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20party%20leader%20D.%20Jayakumar%20said.%20He%20also%20made%20clear%20that%20this%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%20not%20his%20personal%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFissures%20have%20been%20clear%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20of%20late%2C%20and%20Jayakumar%20too%20referred%20to%20these.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20accept%20continuous%20criticism%20on%20our%20leaders.%20Annamalai%20already%20criticised%20our%20leader%20Jayalalithaa.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20we%20passed%20a%20resolution%20against%20Annamalai.%20He%20should%20have%20stopped%20this.%20He%20is%20criticising%20Anna%2C%20Periyar%20and%20the%20general%20secretary.%20No%20cadre%20would%20accept%20this.%20Tomorrow%20we%20have%20to%20work%20on%20the%20field.%20So%20without%20any%20option%2C%20we%20announced%20this.%20There%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20impact%20on%20us%20with%20this%20decision.%20We%20are%20confident%20of%20our%20victory%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-alliance-with-bjp-in-tamil-nadu-now-says-aiadmk-annamalai-doesn-t-wish-101695033292664.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJayakumar%20was%20referring%20to%20remarks%20made%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20president%20K.%20Annamalai%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20criticised%20stalwart%20Dravidian%20leader%20C.N.%20Annadurai.%20Annamalai%20said%20that%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20Annadurai%20criticised%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20but%20was%20staunchly%20opposed%20by%20freedom%20fighter%20Pasumpon%20Muthuramalingam%20Thevar.%20Following%20the%20opposition%2C%20Annadurai%20apologised%2C%20Annamalai%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnnamalai%20has%20since%20stood%20by%20these%20claims%20and%20said%20he%20can%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%E2%80%9D%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%C2%A0cadres%20want%20AIADMK%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20but%20Annamalai%20does%20not%20want%20that.%20Why%20do%20we%20have%20to%20tolerate%20the%20remarks%20against%20our%20leaders%3F%20You%20(BJP)%20need%20to%20piggy%20back%20on%20some%20party%20(for%20votes)%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20anything%20here.%20The%C2%A0BJP%C2%A0cannot%20set%20foot%20here.%20They%20are%20waste%20luggage.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%C2%A0BJP%20is%20not%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20AIADMK.%20We%20will%20decide%20everything%20during%20the%20polls%20and%20this%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fbjp-not-in-alliance-with-aiadmk-will-decide-during-polls-d-jayakumar-8945334%2F%5C%22%3EJayakumar%20continued%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20vice-president%20Narayanan%20Tirupathy%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20final%20decisions%20on%20such%20matters%20are%20always%20taken%20during%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CAnything%20can%20happen%20in%20politics.%20Alliances%20are%20made%20during%20elections.%20Jayakumar%20said%20the%C2%A0BJP%C2%A0is%20%E2%80%98waste%20luggage%E2%80%99%2C%20does%20he%20or%20h