ity%2C%20stone%20steps%20leading%20to%20a%20carved%20gateway%2C%20a%20pillared%2C%20multi-storeyed%20palace%20to%20the%20side.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20not%20to%20be%20outdone.%20%E2%80%9CSlavery%20in%20the%20world%20was%20abolished%20formally%20only%20around%20150%20years%20ago%E2%80%9D%20It%20announces.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20democracy%20can%20be%20complete%20where%20slavery%20was%20in%20existence.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20never%20took%20root.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20should%20advocates%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%99s%20glory%20claim%20that%20the%20subcontinent%20won%20some%20kind%20of%20civilisational%20double-promotion%2C%20skipping%20the%20hunting-gathering%20and%20farming%20stages%20of%20human%20development%20and%20jumping%20straight%20to%20urban%20settlements%3F%20Why%20should%20the%20Indian%20government%20make%20the%20equally%20inspired%20claim%20that%20a%20society%20that%20practised%20(and%20practises)%20untouchability%20%E2%80%93%20a%20country%20where%20compulsory%20and%20free%20%E2%80%98begar%E2%80%99%20labour%20was%20comprehensively%20abolished%20as%20recently%20as%201950%20%E2%80%93%20never%20had%20slavery%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMagnificent%20Bharat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20being%20an%20anthology%20of%20WhatsApp%20forwards%20and%20thus%20a%20little%20more%20crude%20than%20the%20G20%20booklet%2C%20reveals%20its%20hand%20quite%20clearly.%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20iron%20pillar%20is%202%2C300%20years%20old%20and%20yet%20to%20rust%2C%20it%20says%2C%20while%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%2C%20just%2083%2C%20requires%20%E2%80%9CLots%20of%20Maintenance%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20rusting.%20Pascal%20only%20made%20his%20triangle%20in%201600%20AD%2C%20Acharya%20Pingala%20had%20worked%20it%20out%20in%20300%20BC.%20Temple%20carvings%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20boast%20fashions%20%E2%80%9CMuch%20Advanced%20than%20today%E2%80%9D.%20Everything%20is%20competition%3A%20no%20philosophy%2C%20no%20science%2C%20no%20art%20may%20be%20enjoyed%20or%20celebrated%20except%20in%20comparison%20with%20other%20countries%20or%20current%20times%2C%20and%20then%20only%20to%20be%20judged%20superior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20G20%20booklet%20offers%20a%20similarly%20rigged%20competition%2C%20though%20its%20field%20is%20limited%20to%20politics.%20Not%20that%20its%20focus%20narrows%20its%20sweep.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Bharat%20that%20is%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20begins%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20view%20or%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20in%20governance%20has%20been%20the%20central%20part%20of%20life%20since%20earliest%20recorded%20history%E2%80%9D.%20The%20text%20is%20set%20upon%20a%20view%20of%20the%20Milky%20Way%2C%20evoking%20the%20Big%20Bang%2C%20space%20odysseys%2C%20and%20the%20eternity%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flooking-past-the-government-narrative-around-the-g20-summit%5C%22%3ELooking%20Past%20the%20Government%20Narrative%20Around%20the%20G20%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20Dancing%20Girl%20of%20Mohenjodaro%20(%E2%80%9CIndependent.%20Liberated.%E2%80%9D)%20to%20%E2%80%9CPublic%20Participation%20in%20the%20Vedic%20Era%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20the%20Mahabharata%3B%20from%20Ashoka%20putting%20%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20Welfare%2C%20Front%20and%20Centre%E2%80%9D%20and%20Krishnadeva%20Raya%20hailing%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Power%20of%20Participation%E2%80%9D%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20writing%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20elections%20that%20%E2%80%9Ckeep%20happening%20like%20clockwork%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20history%20of%20India%20has%20been%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20ceaseless%2C%20benevolent%20unspooling%20of%20democratic%20principles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReading%20one%20triumphant%20page%20after%20the%20other%2C%20you%20may%20wonder%20how%20the%20authors%20kept%20themselves%20from%20claiming%20that%20Rajasaurus%20fossils%20revealed%20it%20was%20an%20enthusiastic%20advocate%20of%20collective%20decision-making.%20Leaving%20aside%20dinosaurs%2C%20caught%20in%20its%20own%20enthusiasm%2C%20the%20booklet%20even%20allows%20Akbar%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20otherwise%20benighted%20Mughal%20dynasty%20%E2%80%93%20his%20own%20practice%20of%20democracy%2C%20with%20a%20council%20helping%20him%20implement%20%E2%80%9Cpro-people%20schemes%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20328px)%2085vw%2C%20328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195010%2FScreenshot-2023-09-18-at-7.37.38-PM-232x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22328%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195010%2FScreenshot-2023-09-18-at-7.37.38-PM-232x300.png%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195010%2FScreenshot-2023-09-18-at-7.37.38-PM-793x1024.png%20793w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195010%2FScreenshot-2023-09-18-at-7.37.38-PM.png%20802w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673569%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreengrab%20from%20%3Cem%3EMagnificent%20Bharat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20does%20seem%20odd%2C%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20for%20a%20political%20dispensation%20and%20philosophy%20that%20so%20despises%20the%20Mughals%20to%20include%20a%20Mughal%20in%20its%20celebration%20of%20Indian%20democracy.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMagnificent%20Bharat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Enotes%2C%20over%20portraits%20of%20Bahadur%20Shah%2C%20Aurangzeb%2C%20Jahangir%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20Akbar.%20There%20are%20some%20who%20have%20noted%20the%20hypocrisy%20in%20the%20G20%20booklet%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20Akbar%20before%20an%20international%20audience%20versus%20the%20government%20and%20its%20supporters%E2%80%99%20disdain%20for%20the%20Mughals%20in%20domestic%20discourse.%20Kapil%20Sibal%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20face%3A%20For%20the%20world%20%7C%20Another%3A%20For%20India%20that%20is%20Bharat!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Akbar%2C%20as%20the%20exception%20that%20proves%20the%20rule%20%E2%80%98of%20the%20anti-democratic%20leanings%20of%20Muslim%20rulers%E2%80%99%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20historiography.%20The%20%E2%80%98good%20Muslim%E2%80%99%20who%20serves%20as%20a%20foil%20on%20which%20to%20project%20the%20alleged%20atrocities%20of%20his%20co-religionists.%20R.%20C.%20Majumdar%20put%20it%20clearly%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20sole%20exception%20of%20Akbar%2C%20who%20sought%20to%20conciliate%20the%20Hindus%20by%20removing%20some%20of%20the%20glaring%20evils%20to%20which%20they%20were%20subjected%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20other%20Mughul%20Emperors%20were%20notorious%20for%20their%20religious%20bigotry.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20historian%20of%20the%20time%2C%20A.%20L.%20Srivastava%2C%20describes%20Akbar%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%2C%20though%20tolerant%2C%20Muslim%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20as%20if%20the%20two%20qualities%20contradict%20each%20other%20naturally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20nestling%20not%20too%20deep%20between%20its%20lines%2C%20the%20G20%20booklet%20evokes%20this%20very%20idea.%20While%20Ashoka%20or%20Krishnadeva%20Raya%20were%20clearly%20democratic%20by%20virtue%20of%20Indic%20instinct%2C%20%E2%80%9CAkbar%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20thinking%20was%20unusual%20and%20way%20ahead%20of%20its%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20that%20Akbar%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunusual%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20not%20because%20he%20was%20a%20Muslim%20%E2%80%9Cdemocrat%E2%80%9D%20but%20because%20he%20was%20a%2016th%20century%20empire%20builder%20with%20decidedly%20megalomaniacal%20tendencies%20who%20nevertheless%20made%20the%20welfare%20of%20his%20diverse%20people%20a%20principle%20tenet%20of%20his%20rule.%20The%20current%20ruler%20of%20Hindustan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20tediously%20familiar%2C%20and%20his%20brand%20of%20authoritarian%20politics%20is%20very%20much%20par%20for%20the%20course%3A%20playing%20upon%20insecurities%20and%20hatred%20while%20evoking%20noble%20virtues%20like%20equality%20and%20justice%20to%20subvert%20our%20freedoms%2C%20enrich%20his%20cronies%20and%20maintain%20a%20stranglehold%20on%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20give%20examples%20is%20almost%20meaningless%3B%20our%20country%20has%20been%20so%20thoroughly%20disfigured%20this%20past%20decade%20that%20you%20cannot%20tell%20the%20scars%20apart.%20Reading%20the%20surreal%20chirrups%20of%20prose%20that%20comprise%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20know%20whether%20to%20laugh%20or%20cry.%20%E2%80%9CConstantly%20involving%20people%20in%20governance%20and%20decision%20making%20was%20the%20hallmark%20of%20the%20systems%20of%20governance%20practiced%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReally%3F%20In%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F55-english-speaking-indians-fear-airing-political-views-online-fewer-non-partisans-trust-news-says-study-5642667%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20survey%20by%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2055%25%20of%20English-speaking%20Indians%20%E2%80%93%20no%20doubt%2C%20a%20generally%20unheroic%20elite%20%E2%80%93%20were%20afraid%20to%20express%20their%20political%20views%20online.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commoncause.in