night%20in%202011%2C%20a%20sweeper%20was%20cleaning%20the%20streets%20near%20the%20army%20attachment%20camp%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Ferozepur%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManjit%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20drawing%20teacher%2C%20had%20brought%2050%20children%20along%20with%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20the%20camp%20to%20show%20them%20how%20the%20Indian%20Army%20functions.%20On%20stepping%20out%20for%20dinner%2C%20he%20noticed%20something%20strange%20among%20all%20the%20waste%20that%20the%20sweeper%20had%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20a%20little%20closer%20to%20the%20bin%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20a%20dead%20pigeon!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20the%20sweeper%20why%20she%20was%20throwing%20the%20body%20in%20a%20dustbin.%20I%20even%20inquired%20how%20it%20died.%20She%20informed%20me%20that%20the%20bird%20got%20electrocuted.%20Similarly%2C%20another%20had%20died%20nearby%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20four%20days%20at%20the%20camp%2C%20the%2054-year-old%20could%20not%20forget%20the%20incident.%20He%20pondered%20on%20finding%20a%20solution%20that%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20both%20the%20birds%2C%20and%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjit%20converted%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98bird%20ambulance%E2%80%99.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261-5