witched%20to%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20in%201990%20and%20later%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20saving%20birds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recounts%20how%20his%20decision%20would%20often%20lead%20to%20arguments%20between%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20as%20she%20also%20worried%20about%20his%20health%20due%20to%20constant%20exposure%20to%20probable%20avian%20diseases.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20she%20saw%20how%20truly%20dedicated%20I%20was%20to%20my%20cause%20and%20how%20much%20social%20acceptance%20I%20received%20with%20it%2C%20she%20eventually%20came%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manjit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManjit%2C%20who%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Prince%20Mehra%2C%20continued%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20air%20pollution%20till%202011%20before%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Ferozepur%20army%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%20to%20Chandigarh%2C%20he%20printed%20out%20some%20pamphlets%20requesting%20citizens%20of%20Chandigarh%20to%20contact%20him%20if%20they%20spot%20an%20injured%20or%20dead%20bird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20he%20had%20transformed%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20bird%20ambulance.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%2C%20people%20started%20contacting%20me%20and%20reporting%20the%20dead%20or%20injured%20birds%20in%20their%20localities.%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20approaching%20me.%20And%20when%20I%20was%20able%20to%20free%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F170005%2Fmumbai-indian-railway-bird-animal-rescue%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjured%20pigeon%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20treat%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20so%20satisfied%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20contentment%2C%20Manjit%20started%20getting%20recognition%20for%20his%20work.%20In%202015%2C%20his%20name%20was%20also%20listed%20in%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20Records%20for%20saving%20thousands%20of%20birds%20in%20Ch