n%20Games%2C%20along%20with%20moulding%20many%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher-turned-football%20coach%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20starting%20football%20groups%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20still%20functional%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20men%20made%20their%20mark%20on%20the%20field%2C%20Arjuna%20Award%20(1983)%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20(1985)%20awardee%20PT%20Usha%20made%20it%20on%20the%20track.%20She%20was%20only%2012%20years%20of%20age%20when%20she%20began%20training%20in%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Sports%20Department%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Government%20in%20Kannur%2C%20and%20was%20often%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%98Payyoli%20Express%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20speed.%20Through%20her%20two-decade-long%20career%2C%20she%20won%20a%20total%20of%2033%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316259%2Fanantapur-sports-academy-helps-rural-andhra-children-study-earn-livelihood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20medals%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20crowned%20%E2%80%98Sportsperson%20of%20the%20Century%E2%80%99%20by%20the%C2%A0%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOA).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Champions%20of%20the%20Ring%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-15-1695044065.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-15-1695044065.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-15-1695044065-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-15-1695044065-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%