f%20tribal%20students.%20He%20used%20to%20teach%20them%20at%20our%20house%20and%20helped%20them%20in%20their%20higher%20studies.%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20like%20him%20and%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20it%20all%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20862px)%20100vw%2C%20862px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archana%20Nooguri%20with%20the%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%20862w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-300x214.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-500x356.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-768x547.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-150x107.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20Nooguri%20with%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERebbenapally%2C%20where%20the%20school%20is%20located%2C%20faces%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20access%20to%20education%2C%20and%20healthcare%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20When%20Archana%20joined%20the%20school%20in%20November%202000%2C%20it%20had%20just%2034%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Mancherial%20district%2C%20she%20was%20acquainted%20with%20the%20troubles%20faced%20by%20the%20locals%20and%20why%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20the%20school.%20She%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322088%2Fkerala-teacher-gives-free-upsc-coaching-to-aspirants-with-disabilities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransformative%20power%20of%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20these%20students%20attend%20school%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20few%20tribal%20hamlets%20in%20this%20village.%20The%20occupation%20of%20the%20residents%20is%20to%20collect%20raw%20materials%20from%20the%20forest.%20There%20are%20no%20transport%20facilities%20to%20these%20hamlets%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20road.%20When%20I%20joined%2C%20my%20first%20mission%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20come%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Archana%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchana%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20get%20those%20children%20to%20school.%20She%20started%20visiting%20those%20tribal%20hamlets%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20houses%20or%20even%20clothes%20to%20wear.%20They%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20school%20as%20no%20one%20from%20there%20was%20enrolled.%20I%20visited%20them%20daily%20for%2015%20days%20to%20convince%20them.%20I%20told%20them%20how%20essential%20education%20is%20and%20how%20it%20can%20help%20their%20children%20lead%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Archana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20exalted%20the%20benefits%20of%20education%20and%20the%20change%20it%20enables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20show%20them%20videos%20of%20people%20who%20came%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20are%20in%20a%20good%20position%20today.%20Through%20education%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20transform%20their