s%20old%20when%20she%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98543%2Fwater-festival-marine-conservation-india-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escuba%20diving%3C%2Fa%3E!%20Together%2C%20the%20father-daughter%20duo%20has%20collected%20over%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20strongly%20believe%20focusing%20on%20the%20next%20generation%20is%20important.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20am%20teaching%20my%20daughter%20about%20plastic%20pollution%20and%20saving%20marine%20life.%20So%2C%20wherever%20I%20go%2C%20I%20take%20my%20daughter%20along%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20talk%20to%20people%20about%20plastic%20waste.%20We%20do%20presentations%20to%20the%20public%20and%20the%20fishermen%20since%20they%20are%20there%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20beach%20and%20ocean%20clean-up%2C%20his%20nine-year-old%20daughter%20is%20also%20raising%20awareness%20on%20protecting%20endangered%20marine%20animals.%20Recently%2C%20she%20swam%2018%20km%20from%20Covelong%20to%20Neelankari%20with%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20raise%20awareness%20for%20marine%20life%20conservation.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20she%20has%20also%20set%20a%20new%20record%20in%20the%20Assist%20World%20Records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThaaragai%20says%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20diving%20master%20just%20like%20her%20father%20when%20she%20grows%20up.%20She%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20save%20the%20ocean%20and%20the%20environment.%20I%20am%20requesting%20all%20kids%20like%20me%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20and%20the%20streets%20plastic-free.%20This%20way%20we%20will%20become%20plastic-free%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20this%20video%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20their%20initiative%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigur